                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#107rb">Fol. 107rb</locus>: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note states that the Ms. was purchased and donated to the church by ʾabunä Gäbrä Mikaʾel. It mentions also his family members: his father ʾabunä Wäldä Śǝllase, mother ʿUṣǝftä Dǝngǝl, wife Wälättä Ḥǝywät, son Wäldä Mikaʾel and his sisters Ḫaylä Mikaʾel, Wälättä Mikaʾel, Wälättä Kidan.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#113vb">Fol. 113vb</locus>: Commemorative notice for the 12th of Mäskäräm and ʾarke-hymn.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The omitted commemorative notice and hymn are written in smaller, compressed script.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#121vb">Fol. 121vb</locus>: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note has been washed out, but the names of ʾArkä Sǝllus and his wife Wälättä Maryam can still be read.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Smaller script is used on fols. 106vb-107ra, 120-121va.&#xD;
- A text, probably written in the same hand as Additio 3, has been erased: fols. 122ra-vb, 123rb.&#xD;
- Crude drawings: fols. 122v-123v.&#xD;
- Crude notes: fols. 28r, 102ra, 123r.</item>
                     </list>
