               <person>
                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">The name of the original donor has been erased throughout the Ms. &#xD;
According to Additio 1, the Ms. was donated to the church by ʾabunä Gäbrä Mikaʾel. His name and the names of his family members are written over erasures in the supplication formulas.&#xD;
Besides, the names of ʾArkä Sǝllus and his wife Wälättä Maryam, also written over erasures, have been preserved on some fols. (e.g., fols. 38rb, 43vb, 63va, 71ra, 111rb, 113vb) and can be deciphered in Additio 3.</persName>
